# ChainChat License

**Copyright (c) 2025 42Web. All Rights Reserved.**

This work is a project created by **42Web** for educational and exploratory purposes. ChainChat demonstrates how publicly available APIs and tools, such as Zapier, CoinGecko, Etherscan, and other resources, can be leveraged to create private AI solutions for learning and experimentation.

