## About 42Web
**42Web** is a collective focused on showcasing how accessible public tools and APIs can be used to create private AI solutions for learning and innovation. ChainChat is the first project in this initiative, designed to inspire others to explore AI possibilities and learn by creating. It is not intended for commercial use or monetization.

For inquiries, feedback, or collaborations, contact us via [GitHub Issues](../../issues).

